      "name": "Engolir",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Teste de Resistência de Força: CD 19, one Large or smaller creature Agarrado by the worm (it can have up to three creatures swallowed at a time). O alvo is swallowed by the worm, and a condição Agarrado ends. A swallowed creature has the Cego and Impedido conditions, has Total Cover against attacks and other effects outside the worm, and takes 17 (5d6) dano de ácido at the start of each of the worm's turns.\nIf the worm takes 30 de dano or more on a single turn from uma criatura inside it, the worm must succeed on a CD 21 Constituição saving throw at the end of that turn or regurgitate all swallowed creatures, each of which falls in a space within 1,5 m of the worm and fica com a condição Caído. If the worm dies, any swallowed creature no longer fica com a condição Impedido and can escape from the corpse using 6 m of movement, exiting Caído.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
